<div class="gallerytext">
</div>
</div></li>
</ul>
<h1> <span class="mw-headline" id="Variants"> Variants </span></h1>
<p>At some point in 2015, Linksprite started selling an updated variant of the pcDuino V3 called pcDuino v3<i>B</i> (or pcDuino3B). Compared to the original board, v3B updated the ethernet connection to Gigabit Ethernet. Other than that, the board layout stayed the same.
</p>
